Lol, anyway i am having a really hard time and i don't know if i will ever be a successful artist. people say "yeah as long as making the art makes you feel happy and fulfilled, nothing else matters" but i cant be happy and fulfilled if i am not making enouogh money to pay my bills! if i'm making art, success is part of the equation if you catch my drift...i want to be successful in the end. a lot of people get jobs for the growth opportunities, aka so they can become more successful.
